**Entire CLI**
- 生命周期事件统一为 `SessionStart/TurnStart/TurnEnd/Compaction/SessionEnd/SubagentStart/SubagentEnd/ModelUpdate`，事件字段包含 `SessionID/PreviousSessionID/SessionRef/ToolUseID/SubagentID/SubagentType/TaskDescription/ModifiedFiles`：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/event.go:11-42`、`:71-128`。
- dispatcher 明确路由 session、turn、compaction、subagent start/end：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/lifecycle.go:31-60`。
- Claude hook 映射：`SessionStart/UserPromptSubmit/Stop/SessionEnd/PreTask/PostTask` 到 start/turn/subagent 事件；`PostTask` 可带 `ToolResponse.AgentID`：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/claudecode/lifecycle.go:52-73`、`:99-187`。
- Codex hook 只映射 session/turn，`PreToolUse` 无 lifecycle 意义；原始 payload 有 `permission_mode`，但生命周期未使用它：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/codex/lifecycle.go:32-65`、`:68-109`，`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/codex/types.go:29-61`。
- transcript/report：TurnEnd 会准备并复制 transcript、回填 prompt、扫描 subagent transcripts，并保存 `StepContext`；SubagentEnd 会解析 subagent transcript、合并修改文件并保存 `TaskStepContext`：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/lifecycle.go:307-364`、`:408-542`、`:545-587`、`:689-811`。
- wait/notification：Claude Stop hook 等待 transcript flush sentinel，最多 3 秒；SessionStart 可通过 `HookResponseWriter` 输出提示：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/claudecode/lifecycle.go:195-239`，`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/lifecycle.go:100-113`。
- status model：session phase 为 `active/idle/ended`，状态机处理 turn start/end、session stop、compaction；compaction 保持 active：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/session/phase.go:15-64`、`:137-271`。
- parent-child identity：子任务主键是 parent Task 的 `ToolUseID`，启动前写 `.entire/tmp/pre-task-<toolUseID>.json`，嵌套时取最近 pre-task 文件；`SubagentID` 是辅助身份：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/state.go:457-583`、`:589-658`。
- permission/option escalation：Claude 安装 hook 时添加 `permissions.deny = Read(./.entire/metadata/**)`，Codex 安装启用 `codex_hooks = true`；未看到运行时权限升级链路：`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/claudecode/hooks.go:34-35`、`:166-181`，`research/upstreams/entire-cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/codex/hooks.go:147-150`、`:335-369`。

**Orca**
- hook server 负责 loopback HTTP、bearer token、IPC fanout、remote relay ingest、`last-status.json` 持久化：`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/agent-hooks/server.ts:1-12`。
- status model 明确只有 `working/blocked/waiting/done`；orchestration context 记录 `taskId/dispatchId/parentTerminalHandle/parentPaneKey/coordinatorHandle/orchestrationRunId`：`research/upstreams/orca/src/shared/agent-status-types.ts:1-9`、`:55-102`、`:121-160`。
- hook normalization：Claude/Codex/Cursor/OpenCode/Copilot 等 start/stop/permission 被归一化为 working/waiting/blocked/done；payload 提取 `toolUseId/toolAgentId/toolAgentType`：`research/upstreams/orca/src/shared/agent-hook-listener.ts:1589-1630`、`:1751-1819`、`:1836-1933`、`:2202-2316`。
- relay identity：远端 hook envelope 带 `paneKey/tabId/worktreeId/toolUseId/toolAgentId/toolAgentType/isReplay`，`connectionId` 在 wire 上固定 null，由 Orca 接收时 stamping：`research/upstreams/orca/src/shared/agent-hook-relay.ts:50-80`、`:82-109`。
- server start/stop：启动生成 token、hydrate last-status、监听 `127.0.0.1`，POST 需 `X-Orca-Agent-Hook-Token`；stop 会 flush status，但故意不删除 endpoint file：`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/agent-hooks/server.ts:802-905`、`:907-935`、`:985-1027`、`:1027-1184`。
- parent-child/permission 细节：Claude permission waiting 会保持 sticky，除非后续 hook 具备可匹配 `toolUseId + agentId/agentType + tool`，因为同 pane 可并发 subagents：`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/agent-hooks/server.ts:232-283`。
- wait/notification：`orchestration check --wait` 支持阻塞等待并每 15 秒向 stderr 写 JSON heartbeat；`ask` 发送 decision_gate 后按 thread 等回复：`research/upstreams/orca/src/cli/specs/orchestration.ts:23-42`、`:92-96`，`research/upstreams/orca/src/cli/handlers/orchestration.ts:12-45`、`:120-150`、`:305-341`，`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/runtime/rpc/methods/orchestration.ts:249-261`、`:498-562`。
- orchestration identity：任务有 `parent_id`，dispatch 有 `ctx.id`、`task_id`、`assignee_handle`、`last_heartbeat_at`；worker preamble 强制带 `taskId + dispatchId`，完成时发 `worker_done` 可带 `reportPath`：`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/runtime/orchestration/types.ts:1-81`，`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/runtime/orchestration/db.ts:83-114`、`:410-430`、`:563-688`，`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/runtime/orchestration/preamble.ts:44-80`。
- coordinator handling：heartbeat 必须按 `dispatchId` 归因；`worker_done` 按 `taskId` 完成 task 和 dispatch；stale heartbeat 只告警不自动失败：`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/runtime/orchestration/coordinator.ts:221-340`、`:418-574`。
- permission/option escalation：Codex hook 安装会写 trust entries，避免 hooks 进入 review required；decision gates/ask 是人工选项通道：`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/codex/hook-service.ts:297-337`、`:469-515`，`research/upstreams/orca/src/main/runtime/rpc/methods/orchestration.ts:498-562`。

